Dialogs.Dialog: It's sudden. I don't think so.

If I made you feel uncomfortable, I'm sorry.
Yes, it's good. I was a little weird today.
（I wonder if she forgave me. I have to be careful）
Hey, these days... why are you so cold?
About me... do you hate me?
（Hmm, was she hurt? I may have been cold recently...）
I'm really sorry, I won't do it anymore!
Don't be in a bad mood.
Yes, I'm kinda weird these days.
（She forgave me. I have to be careful）
No... It's not my imagination. Because...
Because... I don't know what to do...
（This looks serious... Certainly I might have been cold recently...）
I'm really sorry, I won't do it anymore!
Don't be in a bad mood.
There is no reason to listen anymore.
Haha, don't get so angry. Look, laugh a little.
Geez, I don't like it anymore!
Hey, please? Do you feel upset? Tehe▼

▲高嶺＊＊▲. Excuse me, can you see me now?
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Excuse me, can you see me now?

（Oh, it's▲高嶺＊＊▲... Is she still angry?）

That's not the case... What would I do if you started hating me...
Yup. I saw you doing your best.
Yes, I know I was wrong.
I'm sorry too. But I don't want you to do it anymore...
Yes. I don't want to be hated by ▲高嶺＊＊▲ anymore.
No, even if it's messed up, I started to like it more and more... I'm afraid of it...
Yes, you were doing your best.
Did you? I didn't like it...
I know, because of me. I'm sorry.
I thought I would be hated... I was scared...
I'm really sorry. I made you feel pain.
I was scared... I was lonely!

Eh!? Wait a minute... here you are.
Did you come to visit me?
Yes, it's a little easier. Thank you. I'm sorry, for going out of the way.
It's obvious. I worry about you.
▲高嶺＊＊▲ is always trying too hard. You need to get out more.
If it's for too long, it's bad for your health. It's time to go home.
Of course. Well then, take care.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I hope you get well soon）
（▲高嶺＊＊▲, I wonder how you are...）
...Eh. Um, wait a minute... Please come in.
I'm visiting you. Is it okay?
Thank you. Yeah, it's a lot easier.
I was just bored. I was wondering if I could see you.
Me too. That's why if I can't see▲高嶺＊＊▲, I'll get sick.

Haha, that's right. If you're happy, it was worth it.

Hopefully if you're going to visit me, you don't get sick.
If it's too long, it's bad for you. I'll be back soon.
Yes, I'll come again. See you.

Yes, yes. I understand, calm down.
When you come visit me like this, it's like I'm keeping you to myself, so it's a bit nice.
You want to keep me to yourself, right?
Right? That's why, it's better to be healthy.
I'm glad to see you. Don't you get sick?

Yes, I'm fine. Maybe thanks to your visit.

Let's play a lot today, okay?

You're welcome. Don't over do it, okay?
Yup. But, isn't it nice to go out with you?
That's fine. Let's get along, okay?
As you can see. It was thanks to your visit.
Fufu, let's have a date soon. I've endured it.
（I'm bored... I'm tired of being at home）
I'm sorry if I'm bothering you.
Not all all. I wonder if you were bored.
Correct answer. Thank you for coming.
Oh, it's annoying if you stay long. I'm leaving now.
That's not the case though... Yes, thank you for today.
If you have any trouble, let me know please? About anything.
As expected from you. All right, thank you.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲. I have to get well soon）
（I'm bored... I'm tired of staying at home）

（For▲高嶺＊＊▲, I have to get well soon）

Are you alright? Does it hurt?

Yes, we can't kiss if I don't heal...

Sorry to keep you waiting. Thank you for your visit.

Sorry to keep you waiting. Thank you for your visit.
Yes... I'm glad, don't get sick anymore...
Yes. I'm sorry to make you feel lonely. I like being together.
Sorry to keep you waiting. Thank you for your visit.
I'm glad...Oh, you can't get sick and worry your girlfriend anymore, okay?
Yes, I will do my best.
Let's go play a lot. Then I will forgive you.
